note: Teacher, writer, musician & poet living in Stockholm, Sweden. I originate from the Darling Downs & Condamine River in Queensland Australia. I work across media. I'm interested in language, consciousness, nomadic cultures, music and sound art, Indigenous peoples, psychic separation from the body, the occult, avant garde art, blasphemy, ecology, alternative communities, philosophy, counter cultures, technologies of liberation, body adornment, autonomous conditions & non-dualistic reality.
